    "Quantum Mob/ Q3 Symbol", "language" -> "en", "paclet" -> "QuantumMob/Q3",
     "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "BosonBasis[{b1, b2, ...}, n] returns the Fock-state basis for Bosons b1, \
b2, ... with total number of particles up to n. BosonBasis[{b1, b2, ...}, \
{n}] gives the basis with exactly n particles. BosonBasis[{b1, b2, ...}, {m, \
n}] gives the basis with m to n particles. BosonBasis[{b1, b2, ...}, nspec, \
{k1, k2, ...}] allows for each mode to have an occupation number only from \
{k1, k2, ...}. BosonBasis[b, spec] is equivalent to BosonBasis[{b}, spec].", 
    "synonyms" -> {}, "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> "BosonBasis", 
    "titlemodifier" -> "", "metadescription" -> "", "windowtitle" -> 
